    <h1>What Summit Night on Kilimanjaro Actually Feels Like</h1>
    <p>An honest hour-by-hour walk-through of summit night on Mount Kilimanjaro from 11 PM wake-up to Uhuru Peak at sunrise, what to expect mentally and physically, and how to prepare.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
